==== 賽揚iA與豐田Yaris（四門轎車版） ====
[[File:2016_Scion_iA_(North_America).jpg|150px]]
[[File:Toyota_Yaris_iA_P4250824.jpg|150px]]
2012年11月馬自達與[[豐田汽車|豐田汽車]]共同宣佈，前者位於[[墨西哥|墨西哥]][[瓜納華托|瓜納華托]]的新工廠將幫助後者OEM代工生產5萬輛汽車，以銷往[[北美洲|北美洲]]市場。2015年4月舉行的[[紐約國際車展|紐約國際車展]]上，豐田汽車公開新車款賽揚iA<ref>{{en}}[http://www.caranddriver.com/news/2016-scion-ia-photos-and-info-news Car and Driver: 2016 Scion iA: A Mazda 2 Sedan with a Scion Badge] {{Wayback|url=http://www.caranddriver.com/news/2016-scion-ia-photos-and-info-news |date=20181107161754 }}。</ref>，實為以第四代馬自達2四門轎車版改造的雙生車款，並借重馬自達墨西哥工廠專攻北美洲<ref>{{en}}[http://blog.caranddriver.com/next-generation-mazda-2-and-a-subcompact-toyota-to-be-produced-at-mazdas-mexican-plant/ Car & Driver: Next-Generation Mazda 2 and a "Subcompact Toyota" to be Produced at Mazda's Mexican Plant] {{Wayback|url=http://blog.caranddriver.com/next-generation-mazda-2-and-a-subcompact-toyota-to-be-produced-at-mazdas-mexican-plant/ |date=20180328041356 }}。</ref>。此款賽揚iA除了廠徽標誌不同，前、後保險桿也煥然一新。

2015年9月29日豐田加拿大公司宣佈[[豐田Yaris|豐田Yaris]]四門轎車版正式上市<ref>{{en}}[http://media.toyota.ca/releases/the-2016-yaris-sedan:-a-small-car-with-injection-of-style-and-great-value-for-young-buyers-big-lives Toyota Canada: A Small Car With Injection Of Style And Great Value For Young Buyers’ Big Lives] {{Wayback|url=http://media.toyota.ca/releases/the-2016-yaris-sedan:-a-small-car-with-injection-of-style-and-great-value-for-young-buyers-big-lives |date=20210118070553 }}。</ref>，從外觀來看跟賽揚iA的差別僅在於廠徽標誌而已。動力心臟依然沿用1.5L直列四缸DOHC [[馬自達P族引擎#1.5L（P5-VPS型）|P5-VPS型]]引擎，可選配六速自排或是六速手排變速箱。標準配備有[[巡航定速|巡航定速]]、四門電動窗及電動上鎖，另可加價選購7吋LCD觸控螢幕、6支揚聲器、雙前座加熱座椅與倒車顯影等配備<ref>{{en}}[http://www.carscoops.com/2015/10/canadas-2016-toyota-yaris-sedan-is.html Carscoops: Canada's 2016 Toyota Yaris Sedan Is A Rebadged Scion iA] {{Wayback|url=http://www.carscoops.com/2015/10/canadas-2016-toyota-yaris-sedan-is.html |date=20171220212238 }}。</ref>。

2016年2月3日豐田汽車美國分公司宣布廢除賽揚之品牌，3月23日起改以豐田Yaris之名於該地上市<ref>{{ja}}[https://response.jp/article/2016/03/29/272466.html Response: サイオンのデミオセダン、「iA 」…ブランド廃止でヴィッツの一員に] {{Wayback|url=https://response.jp/article/2016/03/29/272466.html |date=20201115162022 }}。</ref>。
